s. These results demonstrate the power\nof our technique to compare numerical simulations with high-dimensional\ndatasets, and paves the way for using the wider field TESS asteroseismic data\ntogether with the future generations of simulations to constrain the subgrid\nmodels for turbulence, star formation and feedback processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jun 2021 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-30"}
