 timescale to runaway accretion\nis shorter than the disc lifetime as in prior studies. Finally, we discuss the\nimplications of the efficient recycling on the observed chemical abundances of\nthe planetary atmosphere (especially for super-Earths and mini-Neptunes).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jun 2021 18:20:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Sep 2021 20:16:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-15"}
