 proposed BLRM is well capable of mitigating\nlabel noise in medical image classification tasks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jun 2021 10:05:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 11 Jun 2022 12:53:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
